Security Manager Management
Security Manager (Deputy Managing Director) required for a leading Security company in Abu Dhabi. Major responsibilities are to assist MD to provide leadership to position the company at the forefront of the industry and promote revenue, profitability and business development. Provide analysis to all aspects of company to ensure efficiency, quality service, and cost-effective management of resources. Min. 10 years Security and management experience and membership are must. Email your CV to:  sec.manager@yahoo.com  or Fax 026665625.
